39:51.458 --> 39:55.250
♪ BUT YOU DON'T HEAR
A WORD I SAY ♪

39:58.834 --> 40:01.208
♪ IS THAT THE THANKS I GET ♪

40:01.250 --> 40:04.125
♪ FOR LOVING YOU? ♪

40:06.041 --> 40:09.375
♪ NOW I'M TIRED OF THE LOOKS
YOU GIVE ME ♪

40:09.417 --> 40:12.041
(silverware clinking on glasses,
applause)

40:12.083 --> 40:14.041
MAYBE WE SHOULD...

40:14.083 --> 40:16.041
♪ AND I'M GETTING TIRED
OF HOW YOU FORGET ♪

40:16.083 --> 40:18.667
GO TALK TO THE GUESTS?
(laughs) YEAH.

40:18.709 --> 40:21.000
♪ THE LOVING THINGS I SAY ♪

40:23.041 --> 40:26.000
ANYTHING ELSE YOU NEED TO DO
FOR YOUR SPECIAL FRIEND TONIGHT,

40:26.041 --> 40:28.041
OR ARE YOU OFF THE CLOCK?

40:28.083 --> 40:30.125
YOU'RE AN IDIOT.

40:30.166 --> 40:33.041
I LOVE YOU,
BUT... IDIOT ALL THE TIME.

40:33.083 --> 40:35.041
I MEAN, HOW CAN YOU BE JEALOUS
OF ME AND VIOLET?

40:35.083 --> 40:37.125
SHE'S--WE'RE--YOU...

40:37.166 --> 40:39.750
SHE'S VIOLET.
I'M NOT JEALOUS
OF YOU AND VIOLET.

40:39.792 --> 40:41.333
I'M JEALOUS OF ME AND YOU.

40:41.375 --> 40:43.333
YOU'RE ALL UP
IN VIOLET'S WEDDING,

40:43.375 --> 40:47.041
AND YOU AND I CAN'T EVEN AGREE
ON PASTOR VERSUS RABBI.

40:47.083 --> 40:50.125
OKAY. PASTOR AND RABBI.

40:50.166 --> 40:51.959
♪ NOW FAITH AND TRUST ♪

40:52.000 --> 40:53.667
IDIOT.

40:53.709 --> 40:56.625
THERE'S A STORAGE SHED
NEAR THE BACK.

40:56.667 --> 40:58.625
(laughs) I'VE NEVER DONE IT
IN A ROOM

40:58.667 --> 41:00.041
THAT SMELLS OF COMPOST.

41:00.083 --> 41:02.417
WELL, THERE'S A FIRST TIME
FOR EVERYTHING.

41:02.458 --> 41:04.000
♪ OH, WE CAN MAKE IT BETTER ♪

41:04.041 --> 41:06.583
♪ LET'S PUT OURSELVES TOGETHER ♪

41:06.625 --> 41:07.792
SHELDON.

41:07.834 --> 41:10.000
HEY.
CAN I GET YOU A DRINK?

41:10.041 --> 41:13.041
(laughs) WHY DON'T I
GET US BOTH SOME COFFEE?

41:13.083 --> 41:14.542
NO. SCREW IT, SAM.

41:14.583 --> 41:16.542
WE'RE SINGLE GUYS
AT A WEDDING.

41:16.583 --> 41:19.583
THE ONLY WAY TO MAKE IT THROUGH
IS TO DRINK... A LOT.

41:19.625 --> 41:21.709
THE CAKE IS NOT BAD.
WE GOT IT AT RALPH'S.

41:21.750 --> 41:24.333
SCOTCH ROCKS.

41:24.375 --> 41:26.041
(chuckles) YEAH.

41:26.083 --> 41:29.500
I REALLY AM... HAPPY
FOR YOU AND VIOLET.

41:29.542 --> 41:31.041
THANKS.
(clinks)

41:31.083 --> 41:32.875
(laughs)

41:32.917 --> 41:35.041
♪ I DON'T EVER
WANNA FIGHT AGAIN ♪

41:35.083 --> 41:36.291
(sets glass on table)

41:36.333 --> 41:38.625
SOMETHING WRONG?

41:38.667 --> 41:42.625
IT'S JUST...

41:42.667 --> 41:46.583
I'VE NEVER BEEN
ANY GOOD AT MARRIAGE.

41:46.625 --> 41:50.000
♪ ...IN LOVE ♪

41:50.041 --> 41:54.208
♪ OH, WE CAN MAKE IT BETTER ♪

41:54.250 --> 41:57.792
♪ WE CAN MAKE IT BETTER ♪

41:57.834 --> 42:01.625
♪ OH, WE CAN MAKE IT BETTER ♪

42:01.667 --> 42:05.166
♪ OH, WE CAN
MAKE IT BETTER ♪

42:05.208 --> 42:08.041
♪ OH, WE CAN MAKE IT BETTER ♪

42:08.083 --> 42:10.041
YOU THINK
THEY'RE GONNA MAKE IT--

42:10.083 --> 42:11.625
VIOLET AND PETE?

42:11.667 --> 42:13.417
♪ MAKE IT BETTER ♪

42:13.458 --> 42:16.250
DO YOU THINK THE SECOND TIME
AROUND, PEOPLE DO IT BETTER?

42:16.291 --> 42:18.625
I HOPE SO.

42:18.667 --> 42:20.875
♪ WE CAN MAKE IT BETTER,
LET'S PUT OURSELVES TOGETHER ♪

42:20.917 --> 42:24.583
♪ AND START IT AGAIN ♪
